xt": "Biomedical", "bbox": [488.1, 557.9, 565.0, 580.4]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [933.4, 557.9, 944.8, 580.4]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [1081.1, 557.9, 1092.5, 580.4]}, {"text": "Lithium", "bbox": [91.0, 616.8, 176.5, 649.8]}, {"text": "Lithium is a vertically-integrated technology business, based on both", "bbox": [91.0, 661.3, 608.6, 687.2]}, {"text": "inorganic and organic lithium chemistries. While lithium is sold into a", "bbox": [91.0, 684.6, 608.2, 710.6]}, {"text": "variety of end-markets, we have focused our efforts on energy storage,", "bbox": [91.0, 708.0, 608.2, 733.9]}, {"text": "specialty polymers and pharmaceuticals.", "bbox": [91.0, 731.3, 390.5, 757.3]}, {"text": "The electrochemical properties of lithium make it an ideal material for", "bbox": [91.0, 766.5, 608.3, 792.5]}, {"text": "portable energy storage in high performance applications, including", "bbox": [91.0, 789.8, 608.2, 815.8]}, {"text": "heart pacemakers, cell phones, camcorders, personal computers and next-", "bbox": [91.0, 813.2, 603.3, 839.1]}, {"text": "generation technologies that combine cellular and wireless capabilities", "bbox": [645.0, 620.5, 1162.8, 646.4]}, {"text": "into a single device. Lithium is also being developed as the enabling", "bbox": [645.0, 643.8, 1162.2, 669.8]}, {"text": "element in advanced batteries for use in hybrid electric, plug-in hybrids", "bbox": [645.0, 667.1, 1162.8, 693.1]}, {"text": "and all-electric vehicles.", "bbox": [645.0, 690.5, 821.7, 716.5]}, {"text": "Organolithium products are sold to fine chemical and pharmaceutical", "bbox": [645.0, 725.7, 1162.6, 751.6]}, {"text": "customers who use lithium’s unique chemical properties to synthesize", "bbox": [645.0, 749.0, 1162.3, 775.0]}, {"text": "high value-added products. Organolithiums are also highly valued", "bbox": [645.0, 772.4, 1162.3, 798.3]}, {"text": "in the specialty polymer markets as initiators in the production of", "bbox": [645.0, 795.7, 1162.7, 821.7]}, {"text": "synthetic rubbers and elastomers.", "bbox": [645.0, 819.0, 893.7, 845.0]}, {"text": "The following chart summarizes the major markets for various lithium products:", "bbox": [91.0, 854.2, 690.9, 880.2]}, {"text": "Primary", "bbox": [465.2, 917.4, 525.4, 938.7]}, {"text": "Inorganics", "bbox": [456.8, 937.2, 529.7, 958.5]}, {"text": "Specialty", "bbox": [610.2, 917.4, 675.9, 938.7]}, {"text": "Inorganics", "bbox": [604.6, 937.2, 677.4, 958.5]}, {"text": "Lithium", "bbox": [760.3, 897.6, 817.2, 918.9]}, {"text": "Metal/Ion Battery", "bbox": [727.0, 917.4, 850.5, 938.7]}, {"text": "Materials", "bbox": [756.6, 937.3, 820.9, 958.5]}, {"text": "Organometallics", "bbox": [879.7, 937.3, 993.3, 958.5]}, {"text": "Intermediates", "bbox": [1037.1, 937.3, 1131.4, 958.5]}, {"text": "Fine Chemicals", "bbox": [95.7, 962.4, 206.8, 983.7]}, {"text": "Pharmaceuticals, agricultural products", "bbox": [95.7, 981.9, 357.1, 1004.4]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [487.6, 981.9, 499.0, 1004.4]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [783.1, 981.9, 794.5, 1004.4]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [930.8, 981.9, 942.2, 1004.4]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [1078.5, 981.9, 1089.9, 1004.4]}, {"text": "Polymers", "bbox": [95.7, 1006.9, 162.4, 1028.2]}, {"text": "Elastomers, synthetic rubbers,", "bbox": [95.7, 1026.4, 304.8, 1048.9]}, {"text": "industrialcoatings", "bbox": [95.7, 1046.2, 216.6, 1068.7]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [930.8, 1046.2, 942.2, 1068.7]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [1078.5, 1046.2, 1089.9, 1068.7]}, {"text": "Energy Storage", "bbox": [95.7, 1071.2, 204.7, 1092.4]}, {"text": "Non-rechargeable batteries, lithium ion", "bbox": [95.7, 1090.7, 369.8, 1113.2]}, {"text": "batteries (rechargeable)", "bbox": [95.7, 1110.5, 252.9, 1133.0]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [487.6, 1110.5, 499.0, 1133.0]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [635.3, 1110.5, 646.7, 1133.0]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [783.0, 1110.5, 794.4, 1133.0]}, {"text": "Other", "bbox": [95.7, 1135.4, 139.0, 1156.7]}, {"text": "Glass & ceramics, construction, greases &", "bbox": [95.7, 1154.9, 387.3, 1177.5]}, {"text": "lubricants, air treatment, pool water treatment", "bbox": [95.7, 1174.7, 412.5, 1197.3]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [487.6, 1174.7, 499.0, 1197.3]}, {"text": "X", "bbox": [635.3, 1174.7, 646.7, 1197.3]}, {"text": "Industry Overview", "bbox": [91.0, 1233.6, 285.3, 1266.7]}, {"text": "Food Ingredients", "bbox": [91.0, 1296.8, 248.2, 1324.9]}, {"text": "Our BioPolymer business serves the texture, structure and physical", "bbox": [91.0, 1334.6, 608.4, 1360.6]}, {"text": "stability (“TSPS”) food ingredients market. TSPS ingredients impart", "bbox": [91.0, 1358.0, 608.5, 1383.9]}, {"text": "physical properties to thicken and stabilize foods. There are many", "bbox": [91.0, 1381.3, 609.0, 1407.3]}, {"text": "types of TSPS ingredients and a wide range of food groups served,", "bbox": [91.0, 1404.6, 608.8, 1430.6]}, {"text": "including bakery, meats, dairy and convenience products. The industry", "bbox": [91.0, 1428.0, 608.1, 1454.0]}, {"text": "is dispersed geographically, with the majority of our sales in Europe,", "bbox": [91.0, 1451.3, 608.9, 1477.3]}, {"text": "North America and Asia.", "bbox": [91.0, 1474.7, 278.2, 1500.6]}, {"text": "Trends driving market growth include increasing consumer interest", "bbox": [645.0, 1237.3, 1162.7, 1263.3]}, {"text": "in healthier foods, greater convenience and growth in per capita", "bbox": [645.0, 1260.7, 1162.2, 1286.6]}, {"text": "consumption of processed foods in emerging markets. The trend", "bbox": [645.0, 1284.0, 1162.6, 1310.0]}, {"text": "toward health and convenience drives the need for more functional", "bbox": [645.0, 1307.3, 1162.7, 1333.3]}, {"text": "ingredients to impart desired food tastes and textures. We believe", "bbox": [645.0, 1330.7, 1162.7, 1356.7]}, {"text": "carrageenan and MCC, which address this need, are growing faster", "bbox": [645.0, 1354.0, 1162.2, 1380.0]}, {"text": "than the overall TSPS market. The global customer base for TSPS is", "bbox": [645.0, 1377.4, 1162.4, 1403.4]}, {"text": "relatively fragmented and includes large and small food processors.", "bbox": [645.0, 1400.7, 1162.6, 1426.7]}, {"text": "Consolidation among these customers has been a significant trend over", "bbox": [645.0, 1424.1, 1162.1, 1450.0]}, {"text": "the past several years. As a result, TSPS ingredient suppliers such as", "bbox": [645.0, 1447.4, 1162.7, 1473.4]}, {"text": "us, have focused on establishing alliances with market leaders with the", "bbox": [645.0, 1470.8, 1162.9, 1496.7]}, {"text": "goal of reducing costs, leveraging technology and expanding product", "bbox": [645.0, 1494.1, 1162.6, 1520.1]}, {"text": "offerings with key accounts.", "bbox": [645.0, 1517.5, 853.4, 1543.4]}]}